323
00:17:43,979 --> 00:17:46,249
Tampaknya dia bersembunyi.

324
00:17:49,749 --> 00:17:51,590
Kamu di mana sekarang?

325
00:18:00,860 --> 00:18:02,659
Kenapa berantakan sekali di sini?

326
