00:19:05,159 --> 00:19:06,499
Ada apa?

347
00:19:06,600 --> 00:19:08,130
- Kini aku bisa menemukannya.
- Tunggu.

348
00:19:08,199 --> 00:19:10,699
Kamu sudah mau pergi padahal belum makan?

349
00:19:11,030 --> 00:19:13,400
Maaf, aku harus pergi.

350
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:15,239
Makanlah dahulu sedikit.

351
00:19:16,040 --> 00:19:17,239
Pak Kang.

352
00:19:17,340 --> 00:19:20,239
Minta Perusahaan Asuransi Kesehatan

353
00:19:20,239 --> 00:19:23,780
